txt.en: Overrun with the forces of Gorgar the Ruthless, the War of Three Peaks rages at Azgh-buzru.\n\nIf the Gabil'akkâ hope to continue their march on Mount Gundabad, their enemies at the war-fell must be defeated to the last.
You have defeated a vast number of the forces of Gundabad at Azgh-buzru.
You have defeated a vast number of the forces of Gundabad at Azgh-buzru and granted a brief advantage to the dwarves of the Gabil'akkâ.

Gorgar's forces can be found throughout Azgh-buzru.\n\nYou have encountered a vast number of Gorgar's forces at Azgh-buzru, the war-fell. You should defeat them and aid the march on Gundabad.
Overrun with the forces of Gorgar the Ruthless, Azgh-buzru has become the site of many skirmishes in the War of Three Peaks.
